The epic conclusion to the Batman trilogy filmmaker Christopher Nolan, comes to Android, in the exclusive video game inspired by the movie. The EXCLUSIVE GAME, INSPIRED BY THE MOVIE THE DARK KNIGHT RENASCE After disappearing for eight years, Bruce Wayne returns to action as Batman. Awaiting you are mysterious Selina Kyle and Bane, a lethal adversary on a crusade to totally destroy the legacy of Batman.



                                  2014[YahSoft]
